name: Food App - FoodHub (Community)
description:
"Food Hub" is a Food Delivery UI Kit consisting of 70+ pixel-perfect design with light and dark version. The kit is designed for cross platforms.


The kit is easy to customizable including global color and font styles. It has an easy setup and many features that are required in restaurants. We have designed a full solution for a food delivery app. In this UI Kit, we've thought of everything so you don't have to.
